subject: NCAA Basketball Championships (Men)
Basketball (College)
lead_paragraph: Behind monster games from Jared Sullinger and Deshaun Thomas, Ohio State cruised to a victory over Cincinnati to set up a meeting with top-seeded Syracuse on Saturday.
